  <brief_title>Anti Propionibacterium(P.) Acnes Activity of Epiduo® Gel Compared to Benzoyl Peroxide (BPO) 2.5% Gel</brief_title>
  <official_title>Anti P. Acnes Activity of Epiduo® Gel Compared to Benzoyl Peroxide (BPO) 2.5% Gel in the Treatment of Subjects With Acne Vulgaris</official_title>
  <sponsors>
