  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the antibacterial activity of Epiduo® Gel (Adapalene
      0.1% / Benzoyl Peroxide 2.5% Gel) on P. acnes compared to that of Benzoyl Peroxide 2.5% Gel.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
